Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是夢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈？ 請問您這是做什麼
